OL,3,GOrkney & Shetland
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FThis morning will be cloudy
OL,6,Fwith some light rain or drizzle.
OL,7,FOrkney will be dry in the afternoon
OL,8,Fwith the chance of a little
OL,9,Fbrightness, Shetland remaining cloud
OL,10,Fwith occasional light rain.
OL,11,
OL,12,CTonight:FCloudy this evening with
OL,13,Foccasional light rain. Staying cloudy
OL,14,Fovernight with rain more in the way of
OL,15,Fpersistent rain spreading southeast
OL,16,Flater in the night. Freshening
OL,17,Fsouthwesterly winds.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
