OL,4,
OL,5,CWednesday:FCloudy in the morning with
OL,6,Fsome rain. Drier and eventually
OL,7,Fclearer spreading from the north later
OL,8,Fin the day.
OL,9,
OL,10,COutlook for Thursday to Saturday:FDry
OL,11,Fwith bright spells on Thursday, chance
OL,12,Fof rain late evening. Unsettled with
OL,13,Fshowers or longer spells of rain on
OL,14,FFriday and Saturday.
